The package boost-multi-array is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS multi_array)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::multi_array)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_multi_array REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::multi_array)
